---
title: Miso Apricot–Glazed Barramundi with Garlicky Zucchini & Carrot Stir-Fry
description: Barramundi’s delicate skin, meaty texture, and buttery, slightly sweet flavor make it a go-to for fish night. Here, it’s pan-seared for a delicious crispy skin, then coated in a sweet, savory, buttery sauce made with ginger, apricot jam, and soy sauce. It’s served alongside a stir-fry of garlicky carrots, zucchini, and scallion. This lean protein and veggie dinner idea will leave you satisfied (but not stuffed).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/miso-apricotglazed-barramundi-9630db94.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/miso-apricot-glazed-barramundi-64107ac3c624c70b4f0cc723-71cf030f.pdf
